    "summary": {
      "value": "Improve High Speed with bows, spears, and thrown weapons, and deny free attacks."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Rogue</strong>, <strong>Sharpshooter</strong>, and <strong>Weaponmaster</strong>, and must have acquired the <strong>High Speed</strong> Skill.</p><hr /><p>When you use the @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.tiu0D74YNxirN6Tr]{High Speed} Skill to perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a weapon belonging to the <strong>bow</strong>, <strong>spear</strong>, or <strong>thrown</strong> Category, the attack deals extra damage equal to <strong>【your Skill Level in the High Speed Skill, multiplied by 5】</strong>.</p><p>Additionally, when you attack one or more creatures with a weapon that belongs to the <strong>bow</strong>, <strong>spear</strong>, or <strong>thrown</strong> Category, those creatures cannot perform <strong>free attacks</strong> until the end of the current turn.</p>",
